title: Efficient Revenue Mobilization
description: In 2023, Samoa achieved a high CPIA efficiency of revenue mobilization rating of 4.5, indicating strong performance in this area.

title: Strong Fiscal Policy
description: Samoa's CPIA fiscal policy rating reached 4.5 in 2023, reflecting a robust fiscal policy framework.

title: High Unmet Need for Contraception
description: In 2020, 38.9% of married women aged 15-49 in Samoa had an unmet need for contraception, highlighting a significant gap in family planning services.
